% Visual Basic 6 Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with VB6-specific concepts

% File/Module types
Every vb6-compilation-unit is a compilation-unit.
Every vb6-module is a module.

% Type definitions
Every vb6-class is a class.
Every vb6-enum is an enum.
Every vb6-struct is a struct.

% Members
Every vb6-method is a method.
Every vb6-function is a function.
Every vb6-field is a field.
Every vb6-property is a property.
Every vb6-constructor is a constructor.
Every vb6-event is an event.
Every vb6-enum-member is an enum-member.

% Parameters
Every vb6-parameter is a parameter.

% Import
Every vb6-extern is an extern-method.

% Exception handling
Every vb6-error-handler is a try-block.

% Control flow
Every vb6-return-statement is a return-statement.

% Other
Every vb6-variable is a variable.
Every vb6-constant is a field.
Every vb6-reference is a reference.

% VB6-Specific Concepts
Every standard-module is a module.
Every class-module is a class.
Every form-module is a class.
Every property-get is a property.
Every property-let is a property.
Every property-set is a property.

% Access Modifiers
Every public-member is a member.
Every private-member is a member.
Every friend-member is a member.

% Code Smells
Every vb6-god-class is a god-class.
Every vb6-long-method is a long-method.
